title: Dhinamum Ennai Gavani
subTitle: Jai Kumar, a police officer, arrests Rolex, an international smuggler and puts him behind bars. Later, he escapes and the manhunt indicates revenge.

title: Yettikku Potti
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Thangamana Purushan
subTitle: Raja and Subalatha fall in love with each other. However, Raja's father, Aldapu Arumugam, and Subalatha's mother, Kanchanamala, are both extremely greedy and refuse to accept their relationship.

title: Thalaimagan
subTitle: Dheeran, an aggressive journalist, is dedicated to his work and faces many challenges while trying to expose a bottled water company that is causing harm to people.

title: Sakthi Leelai
subTitle: Sage Bhringi worships only Lord Shiva, Brahma and Vishnu. When Goddess Parvati stands in his way, he goes to the extent of giving rise to a demon.

title: Karuthamma
subTitle: A woman, who lives in a village where female infanticide is a common practice, goes to great lengths to get justice when her sister and her newborn child are murdered in cold blood.

title: Idhaya Thamarai
subTitle: Vijay, a short-tempered man, falls in love with Manju. However, he is imprisoned after an incident and upon his release, he learns about Manju's marriage.

title: Chinna Thambi
